OL,5, Talks to resolve a long-running row    
OL,6, with Royal Mail staff over pay and     
OL,7, conditions are close to collapse.      
OL,9,FDiscussions are "precarious" and in    
OL,10,Ftheir "last throes", with the next     
OL,11,F24-48 hours key to settling the        
OL,12,Fdispute, a source close to the talks   
OL,13,Fsaid.                                  
OL,15,FThe Royal Mail board is reported as    
OL,16,Fthreatening to put the firm into       
OL,17,Fadministration if a deal is not done.  
OL,19,FThe BBC understands that there may be  
OL,20,Fmovement on the current pay offer to   
OL,21,Funions to try and resolve the issues.  
